<h3>Sorting the list</h3>
<p>You can sort the list by a single property (as seen in the examples above) or multiple comma-separated properties as shown here. You can also use the `:desc` qualifier to reverse sort order on a property, similar to [Ember.computed.sort](http://emberjs.com/api/classes/Ember.computed.html#method_sort).</p>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-6">
    {{searchable-select
      content=TEDspeakers
      sortBy="firstName,lastName:desc"
      optionLabelKey="fullName"
      on-change=(action "update")}}

    <p>Set by Searchable: {{setBySearchable.fullName}}</p>
  </div>
</div>
